             was indicted for the <rs id="t17681019-43-off250" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17681019-43-off250" type="offenceCategory" value="kill"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17681019-43-off250" type="offenceSubcategory" value="murder"></interp>
               wilful murder of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17681019-43-victim419" type="victimName">
